Singer ‘Omawumi’ Megbele has revealed how she’s been defined by the changes which her body has undergone overtime. The entertainer of Itsekiri descent in an Instagram post shared a bikini photo of herself as she praised her body while appreciating God’s handiwork. The mother of two explained every stretch mark and cellulite on her body has a story. 		 			African men don’t abuse women, children – Seun…		 		 		 			Many nannies, aunties defiling boys – Tania Omotayo		 		 		 			Celebrities that have announced pregnancies in 2022		 		 She maintained that she is grateful for what they represent as they have carved her into the woman she has become today. “Every stretch mark has a story. Every cellulite is important… “Everything has shaped me into this fearless, gorgeous woman that God has perfectly made,” she wrote. Omawumi, since she gained mainstream prominence in 2007 has remained one of the top female performers in the music industry..